<html lang='pt-br'>
  <head><meta charset='UTF-8' /><meta
      name='viewport'
      content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'
    /><meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' /><title>Conta
      encerrada</title><style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Mono:wght@700&display=swap');
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #0f1117;
        font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 16px;
        background-color: #0f1117;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #16181f;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #2a2d38;
      }
      .header {
        padding: 36px 40px 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1d27 0%, #0f1117 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2d38;
        position: relative;
      }
      .header::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #60a5fa, #93c5fd);
      }
      .logo-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }
      .logo-icon {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #60a5fa);
        border-radius: 9px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .logo-text {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #60a5fa;
        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 40px 40px 32px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #f1f3f9;
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }
      .greeting span {
        color: #60a5fa;
      }
      .body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #8b8fa8;
        margin: 0 0 14px;
      }
      .message-box {
        margin: 32px 0;
        padding: 28px 24px;
        background-color: #1e2130;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid #2a2d38;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .message-title {
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0 0 12px;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 24px 40px;
        background-color: #13151c;
        border-top: 1px solid #2a2d38;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #5b5f74;
        margin: 0 0 6px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #60a5fa;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .wrapper {
          padding: 28px 14px;
        }
        .header {
          padding: 34px 24px 26px;
        }
        .body {
          padding: 34px 24px 26px;
        }
        .footer {
          padding: 24px 24px;
        }
        .badge {
          margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .greeting {
          margin: 0 0 20px;
        }
        .body p {
          margin: 0 0 18px;
          line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .message-box,
        .otp-wrapper {
          margin: 36px 0;
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .message-title {
          margin: 0 0 14px;
        }
        .logo-row {
          gap: 12px;
        }
      }
    </style></head>
  <body><div class='wrapper'><div class='email-container'><div
          class='header'
        ><div class='logo-row'><div class='logo-icon'><svg
                width='18'
                height='18'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
              ><path
                  d='M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5S10.62 6.5 12 6.5s2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5S13.38 11.5 12 11.5z'
                  fill='white'
                /></svg></div><span class='logo-text'>Reporta</span></div><div
            class='badge'
          >Conta</div></div><div class='body'><p class='greeting'>Olá,
            <span>{{fullName}}</span></p><p>A tua conta foi encerrada com
            sucesso.</p><div class='message-box'><p class='message-title'>Conta
              desativada</p><p>Lamentamos ver-te partir. Estaremos por aqui caso
              decidas regressar.</p></div></div><div class='footer'><p>Dúvidas?
            <a href='mailto:suporte@reporta.ao'>Fale com o suporte</a></p><p
          >&copy; 2026 Equipe Reporta</p></div></div></div></body>
</html>